author: Brooke Singman, Gillian Turner
title: Australia joins US in seeking probe of China amid questions over coronavirus origin
description: Australia on Sunday called for an “independent international” investigation into China’s management of the coronavirus outbreak and the origin of the pandemic, joining the U.S. in scrutinizing China's role.
